s Program Managing the speech recognition engine used when contacting Apple. \",\"\\\"I know the impact of transformational user experiences: get that right, and you\'ll create brand advocates for life - which ultimately leads to larger shopping carts and higher conversion rates. I look forward to scaling our current solutions and evolving ChatID into a household name.\\\" - Lucky Makropoulos, Head of Product Development at ChatID\",\"Kevin steps into a newly created role as the Head of Consumer Experience, to oversee agent performance, content moderation, and data intelligence. The insights available through ChatID enable brands and retailers to identify trends in the consumer purchase journey, and engage at key touchpoints within that journey; ensuring consumers have the optionality they want, at the moment they want it.\",\"\\\"Our driving force is to make product experts instantly accessible to consumers, wherever they are. I am excited to work with our brand and retail partners to create the shopping experience consumers deserve.\\\" - Kevin Gardiner, Head of Consumer Experience at ChatID.\",\"About ChatID\",\"ChatID powers communication between brands, retailers and consumers from within the retail channel. Our solutions transform the consumer experience, driving commerce activity through conversations. http://www.chatid.com  \",\"Logo - http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20150812/257989LOGO \"],\"answers\":[{\"deal\":\"yes\",\"feedback\":\"Type here...\"}]}','2015-11-23 16:56:20','2015-11-23 16:56:20',NULL),(9903,1,8,NULL,NULL,'{\"id\":\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/csx-corporation-chief-financial-officer-to-address-credit-suisse-3rd-annual-industrials-conference-300182572.html\",\"date_published\":\"2015-11-23 11:00:00 -0500\",\"last_updated\":\"Mon, 23 Nov 2015 11:00:00 -0500\",\"url\":\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/csx-corporation-chief-financial-officer-to-address-credit-suisse-3rd-annual-industrials-conference-300182572.html\",\"urls