eir winter wardrobes, guests can take the phrase \\\"shop \'til you drop\\\" to a whole new level with Courtyard\'s new Chicago Shopping Package. Book a stay now through Dec. 31, 2015 and enjoy deluxe accommodations with a special welcome amenity and a $50 gift card to Water Tower Place. With rates as low as $189 a night, this special deal is a perfect excuse to spur a shopping spree while staying in the heart of the city. \",\"As one of the premier shopping malls in Chicago, Water Tower Place offers a variety of stores that will appease every style, interest and price range. Opt for the large, department-store experience at Macy\'s, or search for something more specific at retailers such as Coach, Vera Bradley, Sunglass Hut and American Girl Place. Take a break from bargain hunting and indulge at one of the mall\'s mouthwatering restaurants, or invest in some entertainment with Broadway Playhouse and Chicago Sports Museum right on site. When it\'s time to call it a day, Water Tower Place is less than a mile from the hotel, ensuring guests never have to lug their shopping bags far.  \",\"Visitors wishing to continue their shopping excursions elsewhere will enjoy easy access to Michigan Avenue from the hotel. Known as the Magnificent Mile, this famous Chicago street holds true to its nickname with an abundance of shopping opportunities on every block. From world-class retailers to local boutiques, guests will find a spot to search for everyone on a list. \",\"After an adventure-filled day, shoppers can warm up while resting their tired feet in the spacious guest rooms and suites at Courtyard Chicago Downtown/River North. Kick back on luxurious bedding while enjoying a show on the flat-panel TV, or catch up with friends and family with complimentary Wi-Fi in every room. Room service, in-room coffee makers, hair dryers and large work desks are among the additional amenities travelers will enjoy. \",\"To book the Chicago Shopping Package, make a reservation online or ca