rformance prepared in accordance with GAAP. A reconciliation of non-GAAP to GAAP net income is set forth in the table above. Amounts may not foot due to rounding.\",\"\\n\",\"Logo - http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20130311/PH74046LOGO-b \"],\"answers\":[{\"deal\":\"yes\",\"feedback\":\"Type here...\"}]}','2015-11-23 21:57:15','2015-11-23 21:57:15',NULL),(10346,1,8,NULL,NULL,'{\"id\":\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/qts-realty-trust-inc-announces-public-offering-of-2000000-shares-of-common-stock-by-a-selling-stockholder-300183536.html\",\"date_published\":\"2015-11-23 16:17:00 -0500\",\"last_updated\":\"Mon, 23 Nov 2015 16:17:00 -0500\",\"url\":\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/qts-realty-trust-inc-announces-public-offering-of-2000000-shares-of-common-stock-by-a-selling-stockholder-300183536.html\",\"urls\":[\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/qts-realty-trust-inc-announces-public-offering-of-2000000-shares-of-common-stock-by-a-selling-stockholder-300183536.html\"],\"description\":\"OVERLAND PARK, Kan., Nov. 23, 2015 /PRNewswire/ --&#160;QTS Realty Trust, Inc. (the \\\"Company\\\") (NYSE: QTS) today announced the commencement of an underwritten public offering of 2,000,000 shares of its Class A common stock by a selling stockholder affiliated with General Atlantic LLC. The Company wi\",\"content\":\"OVERLAND PARK, Kan., Nov. 23, 2015 /PRNewswire/ --&#160;QTS Realty Trust, Inc. (the \\\"Company\\\") (NYSE: QTS) today announced the commencement of an underwritten public offering of 2,000,000 shares of its Class A common stock by a selling stockholder affiliated with General Atlantic LLC. The Company wi\",\"title\":\"QTS Realty Trust, Inc. Announces Public Offering of 2,000,000 Shares of Common Stock by a Selling Stockholder\",\"authors\":[],\"categories\":[],\"copy\":[\"OVERLAND PARK, Kan., Nov. 23, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- QTS Realty Trust, Inc. (the \\\"Company\\\") (NYSE:  QTS) today announced the commencement of an underwritten public offering 