e.com/news-releases/dnaegf-renewal-skincare-presents-two-new-studies-showing-regeneration-serum-significantly-improves-appearance-of-arm-bruising-and-under-eye-bags-300183768.html\",\"urls\":[\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/dnaegf-renewal-skincare-presents-two-new-studies-showing-regeneration-serum-significantly-improves-appearance-of-arm-bruising-and-under-eye-bags-300183768.html\"],\"description\":\"LOS ANGELES, Nov. 24, 2015 /PRNewswire/ --&#160;Renowned skincare line, DNAEGF Renewal, developed by celebrated Dermatologist, Dr. Ronald L.&#160;Moy,&#160;presents two new studies published in the Journal of Drugs in Dermatology confirming that the key component, Growth Factors, found in&#160;DNAEG\",\"content\":\"LOS ANGELES, Nov. 24, 2015 /PRNewswire/ --&#160;Renowned skincare line, DNAEGF Renewal, developed by celebrated Dermatologist, Dr. Ronald L.&#160;Moy,&#160;presents two new studies published in the Journal of Drugs in Dermatology confirming that the key component, Growth Factors, found in&#160;DNAEG\",\"title\":\"DNAEGF Renewal Skincare Presents Two New Studies Showing Regeneration Serum Significantly Improves Appearance Of Arm Bruising And Under-Eye Bags\",\"authors\":[],\"categories\":[],\"copy\":[\"LOS ANGELES, Nov. 24, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Renowned skincare line, DNAEGF Renewal, developed by celebrated Dermatologist, Dr. Ronald L. Moy, presents two new studies published in the Journal of Drugs in Dermatology confirming that the key component, Growth Factors, found in DNAEGF Renewal\'s Regeneration Serum, remarkably treats senile purpura, or bruising, and improves the appearance of under-eye bags. Recognizing the importance of these Growth Factors, Dr. Moy and his team have utilized this key ingredient in their beauty line-up for years.\",\"\\\"I\'m thrilled with the recent studies published by the Journal on Growth Factors, as it is an important component for treating multiple skin disorders in our field,\\\" says Dr. Moy, founder of DNAEGF Renewal Skincare. \\\"We have incorporated the Growth Factor in our Regeneration Serum and the recent studies solidify that we are truly bridging the gap between science and beauty.\\\" \",\"Human Growth Factors, which are bioengineered from the seeds of a barley plant, is proven to thicken skin and improve the appearance of under-eye bags. In the Growth Factor studies recently published by the Journal of Drugs in Dermatology, patients with arm bruising were studied over the course of 6 weeks applying Growth Factors morning and night. Subjects who followed this regimen saw diminished appearance of bruising as the skin thickened. In a second study, Growth Factors were used twice daily on patients suffering from sagging under-eye bags over the course of 12 weeks. Subjects who followed the regimen saw a 75% or more improvement of the appearance of under-eye bags. Furthermore, both studies report that Growth Factors are effective in thickening of the skin which leads to tightening of the skin when bruising is present, and improving the appearance of under-eye bags. \",\"Additional to the Regeneration Serum, DNAEGF Renewal offers a complete line of skincare including a Foaming Cleansing Gel, Intensive Renewal Lightweight Moisturizer, Night Renewal Moisturizer, Eye Renewal Serum, and Scar Therapy. DNAEGF Renewal\'s philosophy of repairing the past and protecting the future of skin applies to all the products under the brand, utilizing DNA Repair Enzymes and Growth Factors. DNA Repair Enzymes are also incorporated into the tinted Sheer Defense Sunscreen and un-tinted Defense Sunscreen, which recently has been shown to be superior at blocking the carcinogenic effects of the sun compared to a sunscreen without DNA Repair Enzymes. Dr. Moy and DNAEGF Renewal Skincare are bringing customers closer to scientific solutions for healthy and radiant skin. \",\"At $145.00, the Regeneration Serum allows you to harness the power of barley-derived Growth Factors to accelerate the growth of