 this investigation, or purchased shares of XBiotech, you can assist this investigation by contacting Peretz Bronstein or his Investor Relations Coordinator Eitan Kimelman of Bronstein, Gewirtz &amp; Grossman, LLC at 212-697-6484 or via email info@bgandg.com.  Those who inquire by e-mail are encouraged to include their mailing address, email and telephone number. \",\"Bronstein, Gewirtz &amp; Grossman, LLC is a corporate litigation boutique.  Our primary expertise is the aggressive pursuit of litigation claims on behalf of our clients.  In addition to representing institutions and other investor plaintiffs in class action security litigation, the firm\'s expertise includes general corporate and commercial litigation, as well as securities arbitration.   Attorney advertising. Prior results do not guarantee similar outcomes.\",\"Contact:Bronstein, Gewirtz &amp; Grossman, LLCPeretz Bronstein or Eitan Kimelman 212-697-6484info@bgandg.com\",\" \"],\"answers\":[{\"deal\":\"no\",\"feedback\":\"Type here...\"}]}','2015-11-24 16:23:58','2015-11-24 16:23:58',NULL),(11342,1,8,NULL,NULL,'{\"id\":\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/olympus-tests-ma-market-engineers-sale-of-psi-300183963.html\",\"date_published\":\"2015-11-24 11:07:00 -0500\",\"last_updated\":\"Tue, 24 Nov 2015 11:07:00 -0500\",\"url\":\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/olympus-tests-ma-market-engineers-sale-of-psi-300183963.html\",\"urls\":[\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/olympus-tests-ma-market-engineers-sale-of-psi-300183963.html\"],\"description\":\"STAMFORD, Conn., Nov. 24, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Stamford, Connecticut-based Olympus Partners is pleased to announce the sale of Professional Service Industries, Inc. (\\\"PSI\\\") to Intertek Group plc.&#160; PSI is a nationally recognized consulting engineering and testing firm providing integrated servic\",\"content\":\"STAMFORD, Conn., Nov. 24, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Stamford, Connecticut-based Olympus Partners is pleased to announce the sal