wned subsidiary bank, Seacoast Bank, and five commercial banking centers. Offices stretch from Ft. Lauderdale, Boca Raton and West Palm Beach north through the Space Coast of Florida, into Orlando and Central Florida, and west to Okeechobee and surrounding counties. More information about the Company is available at SeacoastBanking.com.\",\"Logo - http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20141218/165377LOGO \"],\"answers\":[{\"deal\":\"no\",\"feedback\":\"Type here...\"}]}','2015-11-24 19:07:19','2015-11-24 19:07:19',NULL),(11555,1,8,NULL,NULL,'{\"id\":\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/xyzprinting-announces-huge-holiday-discounts-on-3d-printing-products-300184054.html\",\"date_published\":\"2015-11-24 13:29:00 -0500\",\"last_updated\":\"Tue, 24 Nov 2015 13:29:00 -0500\",\"url\":\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/xyzprinting-announces-huge-holiday-discounts-on-3d-printing-products-300184054.html\",\"urls\":[\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/xyzprinting-announces-huge-holiday-discounts-on-3d-printing-products-300184054.html\"],\"description\":\"SAN DIEGO, Nov. 24, 2015 /PRNewswire/ --&#160;XYZprinting, the world\'s leading 3D printing company, today announced a special holiday promotion, beginning November 27th-December 24th. \\n\\nXYZprinting\'s complete da Vinci 3D printing product line, which includes everything from the easy-to-use da Vinci \",\"content\":\"SAN DIEGO, Nov. 24, 2015 /PRNewswire/ --&#160;XYZprinting, the world\'s leading 3D printing company, today announced a special holiday promotion, beginning November 27th-December 24th. \\n\\nXYZprinting\'s complete da Vinci 3D printing product line, which includes everything from the easy-to-use da Vinci \",\"title\":\"XYZprinting Announces Huge Holiday Discounts on 3D Printing Products\",\"authors\":[],\"categories\":[],\"copy\":[\"SAN DIEGO, Nov. 24, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- XYZprinting, the world\'s leading 3D printing company, today announced a special holiday promotion, beginning November 27th-December 24th. \",\"XYZprinting\'s complete da Vinci 3D printing product line, which includes everything from the easy-to-use da Vinci Junior 1.0 to the unique da Vinci 1.0 AiO (all-in-one 3D scanner and printer), will be discounted and available for purchase through any of these participating partners: Amazon, Barnes &amp; Noble, B&amp;H, BestBuy.com, Walmart.com, Target.com, Staples.com, Office Depot.com, Newegg.com, SamsClub.com. \",\"The following 3D printers will be included in the holiday promotion: \",\"XYZprinting\'s new products including the Handheld 3D Scanner, which is the most affordable scanner on the market, and the da Vinci 1.0 Pro, XYZprinting\'s first open-source filament 3D printer, will also be available for a limited time during the holiday promotion. The Handheld 3D Scanner will be available for $149 (regular: $199) and the da Vinci 1.0 Pro will be available for $599 (regular: $699).\",\"\\\"We\'re thrilled to announce this Holiday promotion so that we can make 3D printing technology more accessible to a broader range of consumers, who may not have previously been able to purchase a 3D printer,\\\" said Simon Shen, CEO of XYZprinting. \\\"With this promotion, we believe we\'ll be able to further our mission of moving 3D printing to the mainstream market.\\\" \",\"Furthermore, from now through December 14th, XYZprinting is also offering registered da Vinci 3D printer owners a one-time warranty exchange offer to purchase the da Vinci 1.0 Pro for $499 through the XYZprinting Online Store. \",\"In addition to the promotions, XYZprinting is announcing new distribution partnerships with the following online retailers: Michaels.com, Quill.com, Frys.com and NFM.com. XYZprinting\'s da Vinci line of 3D printers and filaments will be available for purchase before the end of the year.      \",\"Consumers purchasing a XYZprinting 3D printer will also have the benefit and safety of XYZprinting\'s one-year free warranty, supported by extensive online customer service and useful tutorials on YouTube. \",\"Backed by its award winning 3D printing product ecosystem, the XYZprinting brand focuses on introducing cost-effective and easy-to-use 3D printers for widespread adoption in the marketplace. XYZprinting products require no assembly or equipment adjustments, and provide a straightforward user experience. \",\"XYZprinting has been honored with many accolades, including TWICE\'s \\\"Best Pick\\\" award, Digital Trends\' \\\"Top Tech of CES\\\" award, Reviewed.com\'s \\\"CES Editors\' Choice\\\" award, and PC Mag\'s \\\"Best of CES\\\" award. Its 3D printers have received outstanding reviews from the top echelon of business and technology media, including TechCrunch, Forbes, CNET, and VentureBeat.  \",\"About XYZprintingXYZprinting, a New Kinpo Group company, is dedicated to bringing cost-effective 3D printing to educators and classrooms, consumers and artists, small-to-midsized businesses, and households around the world. With proven industry expertise, XYZprinting has broken down the barriers of 3D printer ownership by providing an easy-to-use device that delivers an outstanding user experience, connected to a computer or via mobile. XYZprinting recently won the COMPUTEX Taipei 2015 Best Choice award as well as PC Mag\'s Best of CES 2015 award. Its printers have won numerous other accolades within the 3D printing industry, at major industry events and with top publications. XYZprinting currently has offices in China, Japan, Korea, the United States and Europe. To learn more, please visit http://us.xyzprinting.com.\",\"Contact:US-PR@xyzprinting.com \",\" \"],\"answers\":[{\"deal\":\"no\",\"feedback\":\"Type here...\"}]}','2015-11-24 19:08:17','2015-11-24 19:08:17',NULL),(11556,1,8,NULL,NULL,'{\"id\":\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/rooomy-partners-with-edberg-solutions-to-bring-3d-technology-to-tri-state-area-and-expand-presence-in-north-east-300184061.html\",\"date_published\":\"2015-11-24 13:39:00 -0500\",\"last