l investors, financial advisors, asset managers, and retirement plan providers and sponsors. Morningstar provides data on more than 500,000 investment offerings, including stocks, mutual funds, and similar vehicles, along with real-time global market data on more than 17 million equities, indexes, futures, options, commodities, and precious metals, in addition to foreign exchange and Treasury markets. Morningstar also offers investment management services through its investment advisory subsidiaries, with more than US$170 billion in assets under advisement and management as of Sept. 30, 2015. The company has operations in 27 countries.\",\"Certain of the above fund companies and online brokerages are clients of Morningstar Research, Inc.\",\"©2015 Morningstar, Inc.  All rights reserved.\",\"MORN-R\",\"Media Contact:Jaime Lyn Aitken, +1 416 484-7868 or jaimelyn.aitken@morningstar.com  \",\" \",\" \",\" \",\"Photo - http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20151125/291219\",\"Photo - http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20151125/291218\",\"Photo - http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20151125/291221\",\"Photo - http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20151125/291222\",\"Photo - http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20151125/291220\",\" \"],\"answers\":[{\"deal\":\"yes\",\"feedback\":\"Type here...\"}]}','2015-11-26 03:23:22','2015-11-26 03:23:22',NULL),(11916,1,8,NULL,NULL,'{\"id\":\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/global-stationary-generator-market-2015-2019---key-players-are-briggs-and-stratton-caterpillar-cummins-power-systems-generac-power-systems--kohler-300184756.html\",\"date_published\":\"2015-11-26 00:10:00 -0500\",\"last_updated\":\"Thu, 26 Nov 2015 00:10:00 -0500\",\"url\":\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/global-stationary-generator-market-2015-2019---key-players-are-briggs-and-stratton-caterpillar-cummins-power-systems-generac-power-systems--kohler-300184756.html\",\"urls\":[\"http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/global-stationary-generator-market-2015-2019---key-players-are-briggs-and-stratton-caterpillar-cummins-power-systems-generac-power-systems--kohler-300184756.html\"],\"description\":\"DUBLIN, Nov. 25, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- \\n\\nResearch and Markets(http://www.researchandmarkets.com/research/qwttm8/global_stationary) has announced the addition of the \\\"Global Stationary Generator Market 2015-2019\\\" report to their offering.\\n\\n\\nThe global stationary generator market to grow at a CAGR of 5\",\"content\":\"DUBLIN, Nov. 25, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- \\n\\nResearch and Markets(http://www.researchandmarkets.com/research/qwttm8/global_stationary) has announced the addition of the \\\"Global Stationary Generator Market 2015-2019\\\" report to their offering.\\n\\n\\nThe global stationary generator market to grow at a CAGR of 5\",\"title\":\"Global Stationary Generator Market 2015-2019 - Key Players are Briggs and Stratton, Caterpillar, Cummins Power Systems, Generac Power Systems &amp; Kohler\",\"authors\":[],\"categories\":[],\"copy\":[\"DUBLIN, Nov. 25, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- \",\"Research and Markets(http://www.researchandmarkets.com/research/qwttm8/global_stationary) has announced the addition of the \\\"Global Stationary Generator Market 2015-2019\\\" report to their offering.\",\"The global stationary generator market to grow at a CAGR of 5.9% over the period 2014-2019. This report covers the present scenario and the growth prospects of the global stationary generator market during the period 2015-2019. For ascertaining the market size and vendor share, the report considers revenue generated from the sales of stationary generators. The report also includes a discussion of the key vendors operating in this market.\",\"Modern power generators are undergoing a series of technological advancements that makes them a lot more unique than the traditional diesel or gas generators in use till now. From advanced monitoring equipment to hi-tech control systems, vendors are incorporating all these features in their generator